The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Bengal | Harass net
                                                                                                                     4                                                                                      Harass net
                            
	Kolaghat, Nov. 6: A Class XI boy has been arrested on the charge of physically abusing his domestic help by blackmailing her with nude pictures he had clicked after drugging her.        
	Kolaghat resident Soumen Panda, 18, had allegedly drugged the maid, 19, on Ashtami when nobody else was home.         
	He had then taken pictures of her in the nude and sexually abused her by threatening to upload them on the Internet if she complained.                                                                                                                                                            
